overview.en: Betriebs Fuehrungs Vorfeldrechner revolutionizes the lottery industry. Based on the Blockchain network, it offers a global decentralized lottery with instant payouts and the ability for anyone in the world to participate, anonymously.
overview.zh: BFV彻底改变了彩票业。基于区块链网络，它提供全球分散式彩票，即时支付和世界上任何人匿名参与的能力。
